node.text: Bring elegance to your athletic attire with this Skirt Sports® Jette Skirt. SKU: 8265109 Transonic Light skirt fabric delivers superior moisture management in a featherweight fabrication. UPF 25+ fabrication protects skin during outdoor activity by blocking harmful Ultraviolet A and Ultraviolet B rays (UVA and UVB). Endure Jersey shorties material is a mid-weight fabric that delivers four-way stretch with superior moisture-management properties. Contrast elastic waistband with continuous drawcord allows the skirt to fit your every changing body. Hidden compression panel in the waistband helps keep the tummy tucked. Front Hidden key pocket in the waistband. Two front pleats on skirt. Feminine front pleats. Block stitching design lines on back of skirt flatter the curves. Built-in shorties have two pockets, one on each thigh to carry running essentials. Silicone dot grippers hold the shorties in place. Sonic Music Port below waistband of skirt allows headphone cords to be routed out from the pocket. 3M Scothlight™ reflective material elements for low light visibility. Skirt: 88% polyester, 12% spandex; Waistband: 87% polyester, 13% spandex; Shorties: 79% nylon, 21% spandex. Machine wash cold, line dry. Imported. Measurements: Skirt Length: 10 1⁄2 in Inseam: 5 in Waist Measurement: 29 in Product measurements were taken using size SM, inseam 5. Please note that measurements may vary by size.
